import sys

n = int(sys.stdin.readline())
a = int(sys.stdin.readline())
colors = [int(x) for x in sys.stdin.readline().split()]

cnt_a = [0] * n
cnt_b = [0] * n

cnt_a[0] = 1 if colors[0] == a else 0
cnt_b[0] = 1 if colors[0] != a else 0

for i in range(1, n):
    if colors[i] == a:
        cnt_a[i] = cnt_a[i - 1] + 1
        cnt_b[i] = cnt_b[i - 1]
    else:
        cnt_a[i] = cnt_a[i - 1]
        cnt_b[i] = cnt_b[i - 1] + 1

if cnt_a[n - 1] > cnt_b[n - 1]:
    print(a)
elif cnt_b[n - 1] >= cnt_a[n - 1]:
    print(colors[n - 1])
else:
    print(-1)
